### 营养素目标计算API测试

# 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

# 计算营养素目标 - 场景A（高目标）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/target/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gender": "男",
    "age": 30,
    "crowd": "普通人群",
    "nutrient_name": "维生素C",
    "scenario": "A"
}

###

# 计算营养素目标 - 场景B（中等目标）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/target/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gender": "女",
    "age": 25,
    "crowd": "普通人群",
    "nutrient_name": "铁",
    "scenario": "B"
}

